{"tid":1380464,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟投票 我地而家其實得番兩條路 想知大家點睇","createTime":"2019-07-29T04:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T07:53:28.000Z","uid":220864,"like":7,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a266b6161c34925a9bcbee5e0523c71ee0642737","tid":1380464,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:31:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鬥長命，繼續示威遊行，<span style=\"color: red;\">班黑警推我地最後目的都係散，但係要令佢地疲於奔命</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打反擊，最大嘅分別就係班當畜龍或者黑警衝，就分散佢地嚟打<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想知大家點睇<br />\n咁先可以比到勇氣前線手足做野<br />\n同埋後排先會明，你地唔係每次一淆就退<br />\n不如多人衝番過去，你唔打都好，班畜龍一定淆<br />\n<br />\n當然大家覺得鬥長命係好嘅都得<br />\n我地玩盡佢"},{"pid":"d32af036fa7502f81d7e850c8e1f11399a128069","tid":1380464,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:31:46.000Z","msg":"定大家覺得有第三條路揀"},{"pid":"cb7e0ec56dc43bef4e34cc8bf7d66846de1edb0f","tid":1380464,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:31:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f31c44f453c8284c21851eecd553031642df5303","tid":1380464,"uid":167506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:32:07.000Z","msg":"搞罷工"},{"pid":"8d302247991dc70d5c20a196d58fa276d5939bf4","tid":1380464,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f31c44f453c8284c21851eecd553031642df5303","tid":1380464,"uid":167506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:32:07.000Z","msg":"搞罷工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:32:32.000Z","msg":"姐係鬥長命"},{"pid":"3a38d9cdeda4bd5485e5d761e1bc90c2029ba710","tid":1380464,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:33:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb787d4579dcfc4ae9faf011464787a7b56ec68d","tid":1380464,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:33:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8